法規內容.條文內容:
The functions of the Wildlife Conservation Advisory Committee (hereafter "Advisory Committee") shall be
1. reviewing and evaluating the list of protected species and the classification thereof;
2. ratifying the demarcation, alteration or abolishment of wildlife refuge;
3. ratifying the use of land within the wildlife refuge zone by major national project(s) (if any) without prejudice to the survival of the wildlife inhabiting therein, and the method of collection of assessment thereof; and
4. advising on matters with regard to wildlife conservation.
